g.text: Fan controller based around Raspberry Pi Pico
Can drive two coolers for two GPUs, cooler A and cooler B
Tachometer signal will be on this pin if
the fan provides it. Measuring that
signal on an oscilloscope I found that
around 20V which would hurt the pico
so I did not use this signal.
